4.Name of some commonly used HTTP methods in REST based architecture?

 •Post->create a record
 •Put -> update a record
 •get -≥retrieve a record
 •Delete -> delete a record
========================================================================================================================
 5. HTML Status Codes ?
 1xx informational
 2xx success; (200 success,201 created,202 accepted,204 No content)
 3xx Redirection
 4xx client errors(400 bad wrong format,401 unauthorized,403 forbidden,404 Not found,405 Method not allowed)
 5xx server errors(500 Internal server Error,502 bad-Gateway,501 Not implemented,503 service Unavailable)
========================================================================================================================
