18.Difference between SOAP and RESTful web services?

 •Both are web services.
 •RESTful use JSON, XML, TEXT, whereas SOAP use only XML.
 •REST is faster than SOAP based web services.SOAP is more secured.
 •SOAP only support POST and GET,Whereas REST support CRUD operations.

