38.What are HTTP Request and HTTP Response?

 Request;
   •Method(post,put,etc)
   •UrI(url+endpoint)
   •Request Header(content-type app/json)
   •Request Body (data to send)
 Response;
    •Response status code.(200,301,400,500)
    •Response Header;Content-Type,Date, Server, Last-Modified
    •Response Body; Data comes from server.





















